# Appended to Wrangler's defaults (.assetsignore, _redirects, _headers).
# Block node_modules folders by default — anywhere in the deploy.
**/node_modules
# Allow node_modules under /trivia-trundle/ so Expo bakes-in icon font URLs
# like /trivia-trundle/assets/node_modules/@expo/vector-icons/.../*.ttf ship.
!trivia-trundle/**/node_modules
